PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of MANITOBA, namely the Hon. A. KERR TWADDLE, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from November 3 to November 19, 1995, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
